package: Zigbee
description: This component handles the retrieval of diagnostic information from the stack
  through the diagnostic cluster. Implement the component as follows. 1. Mark all diagnostic attributes you wish to track as external. 2. Add a call
  to emberAfReadDiagnosticAttribute(attributeMetadata, buffer); from emberAfExternalAttributeReadCallback().
id: zigbee_diagnostic_server
label: Diagnostic Server
category: Zigbee|Cluster Library|Home Automation
quality: extend
provides:
   - name: "zigbee_diagnostic_server"
requires:
   - name: "zigbee_counters"
source:
  - path: protocol/zigbee/app/framework/plugin/diagnostic-server/diagnostic-server-soc.c
    condition:
      - zigbee_stack_common
  - path: protocol/zigbee/app/framework/plugin/diagnostic-server/diagnostic-server-host.c
    condition:
      - zigbee_ezsp
include:
  - path: protocol/zigbee/app/framework/plugin/diagnostic-server
    file_list:
      - path: diagnostic-server.h  
template_contribution:
  - name: component_catalog
    value: zigbee_diagnostic_server
documentation:
  docset: zigbee
  document: zigbee-af-api/diagnostic-server
